Some recent reflections&hellip;
Just show up Half the game is just showing up.
This line rings more and more true to me over time. I got this job because I showed up to the career fair despite feeling really tired. I got recognized for my efforts this past Friday because I showed up. I had doubts too &ndash; will I have tasks to do? will I feel burned out? will they expect me to be there?
